<MudText Class="mb-8">Manage your stock efficiently with our user-friendly interface.</MudText>

<MudAlert Severity="Severity.Normal">
    Track your product levels, add new items, and keep your inventory organized.<br />
</MudAlert>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Key Features:</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    - **Product Management:** Add items to your warehouse.<br />
    - **Real-Time Stock Levels:** Stay informed about your available stock for each product.<br />
</MudText>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Benefits of Using This System:</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    - **Reduce Stock-Outs:** Know what's low on stocks.<br />
    - **Restock:** Earlier restocking.<br />
</MudText>
